{
  "stem": "13382.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whatever father started, I mean, he had no chance to do it, because there was no-- no goods available.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I thought I might try to do something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I went to the wholesalers, who were dealing into this kitchenware.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I asked them, I would like to be a-- traditionally, a traveling salesman.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I got a catalog and I got sort of a price list.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I have-- the little money which we had I took in my pocket.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I got dressed nicely and started to travel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was selling enormous amounts of goods.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, you know, I worked it out in my mind that it's a fortune which I am earning.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Coming back, obviously, nothing except a wooden spoon was available.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was very depressed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, it's-- young people have got so easily to come to sort of enthusiasm.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they see, you know, such a beautiful result of something, and then they cut it off.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so in my desperation-- because I didn't know how long would our money last, really, the way we were.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I passed a street, where there were some small artisans doing all sort of things-- panel beater-- not panel beaters, but sheet metal workers, an electrician.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It's somehow in a cellar under the building.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And as I was passing that street-- I think it was [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Wesselenyi, ?] which was a Jewish part-- I heard some bang bang.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I looked out, and I see an elderly fellow forming, out of a zinc [INAUDIBLE] and sheet-- sheet, some sort of a dish, some big, big, big container.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went down and I ask him, hello, and say-- he was actually-- he was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
